Maven mojos for cloning existing projects using Pax-Construct scripts

          Description

Interface Summary
MavenOptionBuilder Builder interface for Maven specific options
PaxCommandBuilder Builder interface for a Pax-Construct command
PaxScript Builder interface for a build script based on Pax-Construct commands
 

Class Summary
ArchetypeFragment Support creation of simple archetype fragments
ArchetypeModel Replacement for the Maven archetype model, to support non-filtered files
CloneMojo Clones an existing project and produces a script (plus archetypes) to mimic its structure using Pax-Construct
PaxScriptImpl Builder implementation for Pax-Construct based build scripts
